dct_title_s: Chart of the East India Islands : exhibiting the several passages between the Indian and Pacific Oceans; inscribed to the comman
dct_description_sm: Cartographic Details: Scale approximately 1:3,000,000. Greenwich meridian. Soundings give coastal depths, only land relief near the coast is shown. Notes about routes, shoals and islands. Dimensions: 127 x 190 centimeters
